column1: #  Isobel Gilham     - please use these top ten lines to provide  information about the dataset!   Ie explain site,  type, tree  etc.
# Site code = Site + sample type + tree number and sample location (the latter only relevant for deadwood)
# Site =  plot name, Sample type = deadwood (D), soil (S) or living wood(L), Tree number= tree sample is taken from (/5), sample location = base (B) non base (T)
# DBH recorded for dead and living wood
# Missing soil metrics: no soil metrics for sites C7, C8, RO and RM due to  lack of soil sampling equipment
# Missing DBH and length values = for sampling I was not present for (sites RM, RO, GM, GO) tree length and DBH was not recorded
